Description: Prada’s fall/winter 2013 runway collection takes a turn back in time with their romantically elegant pieces. The top has a zipper closure as well as two pockets inside giving you ample compartments for your belongings. Interior is brown leather. Never used, but Minor scuffing on leather and slight aging of hardware from being displayed in boutique. The leather handles have a vintage patina.
